INSERT INTO tasks_subcategories (
                    user_id,
                    task_id,
                    subcategory_id
                ) VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3
                ) ON CONFLICT (
                    user_id,
                    task_id
                ) DO UPDATE SET
                    subcategory_id = EXCLUDED.subcategory_id
